---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="About Hartzog.ai — who we are, what we do, and why we build AI-powered solutions."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <h1>About <span class="accent">Hartzog.ai</span></h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">
      We build AI-powered tools and data platforms that help businesses make
      better decisions, faster.
    </p>
  </section>

  <div class="content-grid">
    <section class="content-section">
      <h2>What We Do</h2>
      <p>
        Hartzog.ai is an AI and data engineering consultancy. We specialize in
        turning complex data into clear, actionable insights through custom
        software, interactive analysis tools, and machine learning solutions.
      </p>
      <p>
        Our work spans the full stack — from high-performance Rust/WASM computation
        engines to interactive D3.js visualizations to production ML pipelines.
        Every solution we build is designed to be fast, maintainable, and portable.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="content-section">
      <h2>Our Approach</h2>
      <div class="values-grid">
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>Data-Driven</h3>
          <p>Every recommendation is backed by analysis, not assumptions. We let the data guide the solution.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>No Vendor Lock-in</h3>
          <p>We build on open standards and portable architectures. Your tools should work wherever you need them.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>Performance-First</h3>
          <p>Speed matters. We use Rust, WebAssembly, and modern web technologies to deliver fast experiences.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>Transparent Process</h3>
          <p>Clear communication, honest timelines, and open-source tooling wherever possible.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="content-section">
      <h2>The Platform</h2>
      <p>
        This site is the hub of the Hartzog.ai ecosystem — a collection of
        interconnected applications, each running on its own subdomain, sharing a
        consistent design system and theme.
      </p>
      <p>
        Our applications are deployed on Azure Static Web Apps with GitHub Pages as
        a backup, ensuring reliability and global performance. The shared theme and
        Web Components make every app feel like part of a unified platform.
      </p>
      <a href="/projects" class="link-cta">Explore our projects &rarr;</a>
    </section>
  </div>

  <section class="cta-section">
    <h2>Let's Work Together</h2>
    <p>Have a project in mind? We'd love to hear about it.</p>
    <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Get in Touch</a>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2rem 0 3.5rem;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-size: 2.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .accent { color: var(--color-accent); }

  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    max-width: 60ch;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .content-grid {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
  }

  .content-section h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .content-section p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 70ch;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .values-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(240px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.25rem;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .value-card {
    background: var(--color-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }

  .value-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .value-card p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .link-cta {
    display: inline-block;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .link-cta:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .cta-section {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
    background: var(--color-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .cta-section h2 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .cta-section p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
    background: var(--color-accent);
    color: var(--color-bg);
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1rem;
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    opacity: 0.85;
    color: var(--color-bg);
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .hero h1 { font-size: 2rem; }
    .values-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
